node.text:
This is such a beautiful story and experience from world class conservationist ! If we could rewild the animals all around the world and protect them like this we would have a solid chance of co-existing together on earth 🌍 @freyaaspinalll @damian_aspinall @theaspinallfoundation GREAT WORK 👊🏾💫
If you guys are looking to donate to a real conservation project that actually puts animals into the WYLD check them out @theaspinallfoundation

node.text: Soon this little guy will be big enough to hang with his troop of other ring tailed lemurs and I’m so happy to see his transition outdoors ! If your interested in this prosimian project check the link in my bio for more BTS !

node.text:
This is such a beautiful story and experience from world class conservationist ! If we could rewild the animals all around the world and protect them like this we would have a solid chance of co-existing together on earth 🌍 @freyaaspinalll @damian_aspinall @theaspinallfoundation GREAT WORK 👊🏾💫
If you guys are looking to donate to a real conservation project that actually puts animals into the WYLD check them out @theaspinallfoundation

node.text:
When you’ve been bit a couple thousand times you learn how to not get bit 😅

4 years old I had my first pet boa constrictor…he was evil 😈! 
Bites in my hands , face , legs , made me cry so many days and nights but I was determined to be his friend after some months of constantly trying to gain his trust we became best friends ! 

Ever since then I’ve been obsessed with snakes of all species / sub species fascinated with their movements the way they eat , breed , climb ,swim , shed , mate etc ! 

Ofc theirs other ways to handle a wild snake 🐍 but sometimes I like to play the game of inches with my eyes 👀 
Gotta see if I’m still sharp 😎

If you have no experience I do not recommend you handle a snake especially a wild snake and definitely do not try to catch him like this because 9/10 times you’ll end up hurting yourself or the snake 🐍 
 Don’t be risky like me 🙏🏾
